Invocation Name: geo guesser
des: Geo Guesser is a geography game which takes you on a journey around the world and challenges your ability to know your surroundings. It will ask you 5 question about different areas in the world and you have to answer it correct to score a point. To play the game just say, "Alexa open Geo Guesser"
